Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Royal Jubilee
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407h3f
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Jun 1977
US view of Queen's Jubilee. Mrs Carter visits Latin America. Anti-gay vote in Florida. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less